[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "石化の息は、晴れたか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01674",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "タイニー……！　クソッ、やっぱりお前に\nついていてやれば……！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01675",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "折れない顔をした石像は生意気だが、\nこの恐怖に怯えた顔の石像はいいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01676",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "てめえ、７回殺しても飽き足りねえ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01677",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "なんだ、別働隊がいたのか。\nそれぐらいは頭を使ってくるか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01678",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺は寛大だ。頭を下げて服従するか、\n一緒に石像になるか、選ばせてやるぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01679",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "チッ……好き勝手言ってくれやがる……\nけど、興味を持ってくれたのはありがたいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01680",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "石像にできるもんならしてみやがれ！\n俺もなりたくはないんでね、全力で抵抗してやる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01681",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "面白い武器じゃないか。それならば石の息を貫ける。\nだが、肝心の自身の身が危ういぞ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01682",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "簡単だよ。息より先に別のもので満たしちまえばいい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01683",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ほう、そんな手があったか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01684",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ったく、タイニー、重くなりやがったな……\nって、これ石になっても聞こえてたらヤバいか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01685",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "チッ、持っていけるのは１人が限度だね……\nそれじゃあ私は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01686",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "させん！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01687",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "んなっ！？　こいつ、見えてんの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01688",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょっと、私を忘れないでよねっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01689",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ナナか、お前は後で遊んでやる。\nもうちょっと待っていろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01690",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "嫌だね！　今遊んでよ、お兄ちゃん！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01691",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "シトリン、アタシらもやるよ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01692",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "シトリン、お前、また俺にお仕置きされたいのか？\n分からされたいのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01693",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ぐっ……い、いや、僕は",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01694",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "決めた、お前はお仕置きだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01695",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "なっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01696",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ど、どっち道そうなるなら、やってやる！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01697",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "まったく……手の掛かる奴らだ。\n今一度兄の偉大さを分からせてやる必要があるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01698",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ちょうどいい機会だ。とことん打ち据えてやる。\nお前たちが参ったと言うまでな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01699",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "なに、殺しはしない。\n……死んだほうがマシだと思うかもしれんが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01700",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ここは私たちが引き受ける！\n今はいったん逃げて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01701",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "っ、そうする！　この石化を解く薬を\nなんとか用意して戻ってくるから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01702",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "それまで持ちこたえてくれよ、相棒！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01703",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なるべく早く戻ってきてよ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01704",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ふ、一人だけ持ち帰ったところでどうなる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01705",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "パルメ族に選ばれた錬金術士といっても、\n所詮はこの程度か",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01706",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "やはり、この星を任せられる器ではない……\n英雄ヘルト様が「管理」してやらねばな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01707",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "まだ終わってないでしょ！\n私たちに参ったって言わせてみなさいよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01708",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "\n",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "雷鳴の島決戦、初戦は惨敗……だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01709",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "8640319422770506679",
		"text": "ああ……だが、まだ完全に負けたわけじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01710",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "8640319422770506679",
		"text": "タイニー、絶対に助けてやるからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01711",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]